\c 12
\s Kuzvipa kunaMwari
\p
\v 1 Naizvozvo ndinokugombedzerai hama, netsitsi dzaMwari, kuti mukumikidze miviri yenyu, \add chive\add* chibayiro chipenyu, chitsvene, chinogamuchirika kuna Mwari, ndiko kunamata kwenyu kunonzwisisika.
\v 2 Musaenzaniswa nenyika ino; asi mushandurwe fungwa dzenyu dzichivandudzwa, kuti muidze muzive kuda kwaMwari kwakanaka, kunogamuchirika kwakazara.
\s Zvipo zvaMwari noRudo kunavamwe
\p
\v 3 Nokuti nenyasha dzandakapiwa, ndinoti kunomumwe nomumwe uri pakati penyu, kuti arege kuzvifunga \add kuti\add* mukuru kupfuvura paanofanira kufunga napo; asi afunge nokufunga kwakachenjera, mumwe nomumwe nechiyero chokutenda sezvaakagoverwa naMwari.
\v 4 Nokuti sezvatinemitezo mizhinji pamuviri mumwe, asi mitezo yose hainebasa rakafanana;
\v 5 saizvozvo isu, \add tiri\add* vazhinji, tiri muviri mumwe munaKristu, mumwe nomumwe ari mutezo womumwe.
\v 6 Uye tinezvipo zvakasiyana, maererano nenyasha dzinopiwa kwatiri; kana kuri kuporofita, \add ngatiprofite\add* zvakaenzana nokutenda kwedu;
\v 7 kana kuri kushumira, \add ngazvivonekwe\add* pakushumira; kana unodzidzisa, pakudzidzisa;
\v 8 kana unoraira, pakuraira; unopa, \add ngaape\add* nomoyo wose; unotonga \add ngaatonge\add* nokushingaira; unoitira ngoni, nomufaro.
\v 9 Rudo ngaruve rwechokwadi. Vengai zvakaipa; muchinamatira zvakanaka.
\v 10 Dananai nomoyo muchena nerudo rwehama; pakukudzana muchikundana.
\v 11 Regai kuva novusimbe pakushingaira; mupise pamweya; muchishumira Ishe;
\v 12 muchifara patariro; tsungirirai pakutambudzika; muchirambira mukunyengetera;
\v 13 govanai navatsvene pakushaiwa kwavo; itirai vaeni rudo.
\v 14 Ropafadzai vanokutambudzai; ropafadzai, musatuka.
\v 15 Farai navanofara; chemai navanochema.
\v 16 Ivai nomoyo mumwe pakati penyu. Musatsvaka zvinorumbidzwa, asi mufambidzane navanozvininipisa. Musati pamoyo yenyu makachenjera.
\v 17 Musatsiva munhu chakaipa kana akakuitirai chakaipa. Tsvakai zvakarurama pamberi pavanhu vose.
\v 18 Kana zvichibvira, pamunogona napo, ivai norugare navanhu vose.
\v 19 Musatsiva, vadikamwa, asi munzvenge kutsamwa; nokuti kwakanyorwa, kuchinzi: kutsiva ndokwangu, ini ndicharipira ndizvo zvinoreva Ishe.
\v 20 Asi kana muvengi wako aziya, umupe kudya; kana afa nenyota, umupe kumwa; nokuti kana uchiita izvozvo, uchatutira mazimbe omoto pamusoro wake.
\v 21 Usakundwa nezvakaipa, asi ukunde zvakaipa nezvakanaka.
